    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Me, You and Kaiju, battle against your friends in an action-packed, asymmetric, local-multiplayer party game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you step into VR as the mighty Kaiju to wreak havoc &amp; squash your puny friends? Or will you pick up a controller, jump in a chopper and take to the skies with your buddies to take down the Kaiju and save Earth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 4 players can grab a gamepad and enter a deathmatch against the VR-controlled Kaiju</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of various different vehicles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the level, flanking the Kaiju, and peppering it with artillery while dodging the onslaught of attacks it’s throwing back at you </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/a7663f92b50a7b6647cfa29f328343d4.poster.avif?t=1766126541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/a7663f92b50a7b6647cfa29f328343d4.webm?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/a7663f92b50a7b6647cfa29f328343d4.mp4?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/786d8086c89f2d6e88737a3472f5c51a.poster.avif?t=1766126541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/786d8086c89f2d6e88737a3472f5c51a.webm?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/786d8086c89f2d6e88737a3472f5c51a.mp4?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take control of the kaiju and experience being a giant in VR</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your surroundings as ammunition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge and block projectiles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your special attack to unleash havoc across the city</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as different kaiju’s each with their own unique powers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/9a357b0087e2b75aaf3ed4d036390916.poster.avif?t=1766126541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/9a357b0087e2b75aaf3ed4d036390916.webm?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/9a357b0087e2b75aaf3ed4d036390916.mp4?t=1766126541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Currently Available E.A. Content:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 playable Kaiju (Bloodshot &amp; Squizzard)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 playable vehicles (Helicopter &amp; Drone)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 game mode (Team Death Match)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 level (City)</p></li></ul>",
